+  // ── Private ───────────────────────────────────────────────
+
+  /**
+   * Decrypt an API-key vault (AES-256-GCM).
+   * Layout: [16-byte IV][ciphertext][16-byte auth-tag]
+   * Key derived via PBKDF2 with salt = "rvfa-vault-{name}".
